com.xilinx.rapidwright.edif

Class BinaryEDIFWriter

  • Object
    • com.xilinx.rapidwright.edif.BinaryEDIFWriter

  • public class BinaryEDIFWriter
extends Object
    A Writer for the RapidWright Binary EDIF Format Provides a binary alternative to textual EDIF that is ~10-15X smaller and loads 5-10X faster. This is intended as a cached version of text-based EDIF as it cannot be read by Vivado. One additional tradeoff is that it takes about 2.5-3X longer to write than text-based EDIF.

      • createStringMap

        public static Map<String,Integer> createStringMap(EDIFNetlist netlist)
        This method iterates over an entire EDIFNetlist to enumerate all Strings. This is done to provide a fast lookup array at the front of the file when loading the Binary EDIF.
        Parameters:
        netlist - The netlist to include in the String map.
        Returns:
        A new map keyed by all unique strings in the netlist mapped to unique integers.
